{"tid":1562613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫管局都係一條重要戰線 仆你個街唔好以為無人唔記得你啲衰野","createTime":"2019-09-12T05:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T05:55:40.000Z","uid":69525,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a3c56cba6b8290fd8687c83bd13548ad26a2c048","tid":1562613,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:31:07.000Z","msg":"我知好多醫護係自己人 多謝你地<br />\n所以我係屌醫管局同班仆街死藍絲<br />\n<br />\n仆街你臭街 醫管局同警狗一樣咁撚賤<br />\n唔好以為少人提左 你就可以置身事外<br />\n由612開始 醫管局外洩病人私隱一直都係核彈<br />\n外洩病人私隱同資料 / 警狗可以自己直接係醫院電腦搵示威者 / 隨意係醫院拉人 / 醫管局個電腦系統直通警狗局個電腦系統<br />\n淨係呢幾單野已經可以推上國際層面 <br />\n係國際層面上外洩病人私隱同黑警濫暴一樣 <br />\n甚至更加嚴重<br />\n<br />\n[經典重溫] 警訊介紹醫管局資料如何與警務處分享<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242913</a><br />\n陳沛然議員：醫管局的電腦系統和警務處的電腦系統是相連的<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242809\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242809</a><br />\n醫管局帶頭破壞醫患關係<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1222430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1222430</a><br />\n急！陳沛然醫生記招懶人包！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1235735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1235735</a><br />\n<br />\n但你今次搞我地既家姐? (爆眼少女)<br />\n連佢都未拎到個medical report 你竟然直接係2日內交左比警狗 仲要係無家姐一家人既回覆 HA同警狗到底憑咩咁猖狂? 如果今次單野既裁決係判家姐輸數 即係同全世界講 警權大撚曬 唔使再跟規矩程序做野 <br />\n推撚到醫管局出黎開記招回應事件 <br />\n咪撚以為縮埋就無人唔記得你<br />\n[有圖]「白色恐怖」大搜捕之夜 公開警方俾家姐信件！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1520172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1520172</a><br />\n<br />\n大家係6月果期屌完一排之後好似無左件事 <br />\n政府已經開始計劃緊清算醫管局 <br />\n以後醫管局既白色恐怖只會越黎越嚴重<br />\n希望大家千其唔好浪費左陳沛然議員既一番心意 尋日更加有一班醫護用實名登報<br />\n林鄭開了第一槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1562178\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1562178</a><br />\n<br />\n推撚到醫管局出黎開記招回應<br />\n另外請大家加入國際文宣戰線<br />\n轉用twitter 罷用facebook<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=9718042a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n最後一句<br />\n你敢搞家姐佢地一家 香港人同你玩真暴動"},{"pid":"32c2e23bbde2aa3548c108d48d0aaf1ae05a5457","tid":1562613,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:31:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"d03d4a5ec06c497fa455da5f9fadeba19ea174ca","tid":1562613,"uid":17954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:33:00.000Z","msg":"醫管局黎緊12 月好似換個紅底入去"},{"pid":"deabaaf836e5a69436aeb3be6d5240afd53ebf1d","tid":1562613,"uid":227405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad5815d89951882033fab9c940bc031f9810767","tid":1562613,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d03d4a5ec06c497fa455da5f9fadeba19ea174ca","tid":1562613,"uid":17954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:33:00.000Z","msg":"醫管局黎緊12 月好似換個紅底入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:34:16.000Z","msg":"係 我都有提到"},{"pid":"e327